- cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are relevant categories as the paper discusses the use of deep learning techniques for grasping.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still relevant as the paper discusses the integration of a simulator and dataset for robotic grasping.
